    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/ba32e422f3ba10cc80da9174ccca71bf.webp?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...he's just been turned into a vampire. Well, actually, he has two problems, because he's also found himself on Fledgling Manor, the hottest vampire reality show in America.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight new vampires are forced to live together in a remote mansion. Each episode, they must vote off one of their fellow Fledglings. But the losing contestant isn't just forced to leave the show — they're executed for the pleasure of the viewing audience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Rocky live long enough to figure out what happened to him? How will he deal with his fellow Fledglings? <strong>Find out in Fledgling Manor, a supernatural horror visual novel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/f8bedb8f0ae3319ad9644f76b44aa392.webp?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=59 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three romance-able characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 120,000 words long</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight different characters to get to know and condemn to death</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Striking black and white visual style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack by kendall :3</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three routes, each with unique CGs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Half a dozen possible endings (including some bad ends ;)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/e92fcbd29cde275275e1ed31eb69dcf6.webp?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/9c20998cf4232114c19908f06e545ddf.avif?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our  <strong>Protagonist</strong> is a grocery delivery app driver, avid reality show viewer, and former bass player for a local metal band. He's also the proud owner of a white 2004 Toyota Corolla! But Rocky was turned into a vampire under mysterious circumstances... How did he get here!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/b5bd1e6fb22947ec4297d52507d29d42.avif?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Possible Love Interest</strong> Aanya hunted the streets of Atlanta for victims while dressed as a nurse before she was caught and put on <i>Fledgling Manor</i>. What's hiding behind her warm exterior?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/d73af7a7c535e02f5fe57b51a9aad9ec.avif?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Possible Love Interest</strong> Eight has a mysterious past, a creepy mask, and... a very friendly personality! Where did they come from, and why are they here?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238510/extras/7a5407d194ec26c804b76f54c1e0a508.avif?t=1760146622\" width=577 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Possible Love Interest</strong> Stefan doesn't understand TV shows and certainly doesn't want to be part of one. Get out of his way. He's got hunting to do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>ALSO FEATURING:</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tay (22) a Christianity and candles influencer, Grace (50) a corporate girlboss, Jason (24) a grindset hunk, Lilia (23) a sad Canadian.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >with special appearances by Niko and Bug, from artist+character designer Shaydh's comic <i>And the Streets Awash in Blood</i>.</p>",
